-- SIX Group Will Remain Independent, CEO Gomez Tells NZZ
-- B y   G i l e s   B r o o m
-- 2011-12-25T10:26:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-25/six-group-will-remain-independent-ceo-gomez-tells-nzz.html
SIX Swiss Exchange Ltd. Chairman
Peter Gomez said the firm will remain independent and a sale of
the company is not an option,  NZZ am Sonntag  reported.  SIX, which operates the Zurich stock exchange, could buy a
foreign clearing and settlement organization or expand its cards
business, Gomez told the Swiss newspaper in an interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Giles Broom in Geneva at 
 gbroom@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
